# Travel Guide App

A personalized travel guide app that matches users with guide personas for local recommendations.

## Quick Context
- **Core Feature**: "Right Now" guided flow for immediate recommendations
- **Key Components**: Guide personas, venue database, matching system
- **Current Phase**: Prototyping

## Key Features
- Personalized guide matching
- "Right Now" guided recommendation flow
- Local venue database
- Guide persona profiles

## Development Status
- [x] Initial concept documentation
- [x] Guide persona schema
- [x] Venue database structure
- [ ] Prototype Phase 1
- [ ] User testing

